custom_steps:
AND I have the following query for the Mets Newsletter:
query GetNewsletterPageConfig($locale: String!, $preview: Boolean = false, $pageConfigId: String, $hasPageConfigId: Boolean!) {
  moduleConfig: pageConfigurationCollection(
    locale: $locale
    preview: $preview
    where: {internalName: $pageConfigId}
    limit: 1
  ) {
    items @include(if: $hasPageConfigId) {
      __typename
      internalName
      configsModulesCollection {
        __typename
        items {
          __typename
          ... on CF_NewsletterModule {
            __typename
            title
            description
          }
        }
      }
    }
    __typename
  }
}

AND the variables are:
{"preview":true,"hasPageConfigId":true,"locale":"en-US","pageConfigId":"t121-homepage-page-config"}

WHEN I make an HTTP request to: https://data-graph-beta.mlb.com/graphql

